quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  17,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  17,1,"pak hai woh jo le gaya aik raat apne bande ko masjid haraam se daur ki uss masjid taq jis ke mahol ko is ne barket di hai, taakay usay apni kuch nshanyon ka mushahida karaye haqeeqat mein wohi hai sab kuch suneney aur dekhnay wala"
  17,2,"hum ne iss se pehlay moose ko kitaab di thi aur ussay bani Israel ke liye zareya hadaayat banaya tha, iss takeed ke sath ke mere siwa kisi ko apna wakeel nah banana"
  17,3,"tum unn logon ki aulaad ho jinhein hum ne Nooh ke sath kashti par sawaar kya tha, aur Nooh aik shukar guzaar bandah tha"
  17,4,phir hum ne apni kitaab mein bani Israel ko iss baat par bhi mutnabba kar diya tha ke tum do martaba zameen mein fasaad azeem barpaa karo ge aur barri sar kashi dikhao ge
  17,5,"aakhir kaar jab unn mein se pehli sar kashi ka mauqa paish aaya, to ae bani Israel , hum ne tumahray muqablay par apne aisay bande uthaye jo nihayat zor aawar thay aur woh tumahray malik mein ghis kar har taraf phail gay yeh aik wada tha jisay poora ho kar hi rehna tha"
  17,6,iss ke baad hum ne tumhe unn par ghlbe ka mauqa day diya aur tumhe maal aur aulaad se madad di aur tumhari tadaad pehlay se barha di
  17,7,"dekho! tum ne bhalai ki to woh tumahray apne hi liye bhalai thi, aur buraiee ki to woh tumhari apni zaat ke liye buraiee saabit hui phir jab dosray waday ka waqt aaya to hum ne dosray dushmanon ko tum par musallat kya taakay woh tumahray chehray bigaar den aur masjid ( beeet almuqaddas ) mein usi terhan ghis jayen jis terhan pehlay dushman ghse thay aur jis cheez par un ka haath parre ussay tabah kar ke rakh den"
  17,8,"ho sakta hai ke ab tumhara rab tum par reham kere, lekin agar tum ne phir apni sabiq rawish ka iada kya to hum bhi par apni saza ka iada karen ge, aur ka fir Nemat logon ke liye hum ne jahannum ko qaid khanah bana rakha hai"
  17,9,haqeeqat yeh hai ke yeh quran woh raah dekhata hai jo bilkul seedhi hai jo lau g usay maan kar bhallay kaam karne lagen inhen yeh basharat deta hai ke un ke liye bara ajar hai
  17,10,aur jo log akhirat ko nah manen inhen yeh khabar deta hai ke un ke liye hum ne dard naak azaab muhayya kar rakha hai
  17,11,ensaan shar uss terhan mangta hai jis terhan kher maangni chahiye ensaan bara hi jald baz waqay howa hai
  17,12,"dekho, hum ne raat aur din ko do nishanain banaya hai raat ki nishani ko hum ne be noor banaya, aur din ki nishani ko roshan kar diya taakay tum apne rab ka fazl talaash kar sakuu aur mah o saal ka hisaab maloom kar sakuu isi terhan hum ne har cheez ko allag allag mummies kar ke rakha hai"
  17,13,"har ensaan ka shagoon hum ne uss ke apne gilaay mein latka rakha hai, aur qayamat ke roz hum aik noshta uss ke liye nikalen ge jisay woh khuli kitaab ki terhan paye ga"
  17,14,"parh apna nama aamaal, aaj apna hisaab laganay ke liye to khud hi kaafi hai"
  17,15,"jo koi raah raast ikhtiyar kere is ki raast rawi is ke apne hi liye mufeed hai, aur jo gumraah ho is ki gumraahi ka waba l- usi par hai koi boojh uthany wala dosray ka boojh nah uthaye ga aur hum azaab dainay walay nahi hain jab taq ke ( logon ko haq o baatil ka farq samjhane ke liye ) aik pegham Bar nah bhaij den"
  17,16,"jab hum kisi bastii ko halaak karne ka iradah karte hain to is ke khushaal logon ko hukum dete hain aur woh is mein nafarmaniyan karne lagtay hain, tab azaab ka faisla is bastii par chaspan ho jata hai aur hum usay barbaad kar ke rakh dete hain"
  17,17,"dekh lau, kitni hi naslen hain jo Nooh ke baad hamaray hukum se halaak huien tera rab apne bundon ke gunaaho se poori terhan bakhabar hai aur sab kuch dekh raha hai"
  17,18,"jo koi Ajila ka khawahish mand ho, usay yahin hum day dete hain jo kuch bhi jisay dena chahain, phir is ke masqoom mein jahannum likh dete hain jisay woh tapayga malamat zada aur rehmat se mahroom ho kar"
  17,19,"aur jo akhirat ka khawahish mand ho aur is ke liye sae kere jaisi ke is ke liye sae karni chahiye, aur ho woh momin, to aisay har shakhs ki sae mashkoor hogi"
  17,20,"inn ko bhi aur unn ko bhi, dono fareeqon ko hum ( duniya mein ) samaan zeist diye ja rahay hain, yeh tairay rab ka atiyah hai, aur tairay rab ki ataa ko roknay wala koi nahi hai"
  17,21,"magar dekh lau, duniya hi mein hum ne aik giroh ko dosray par kaisi fazeelat day rakhi hai, aur akhirat mein uss ke darjay aur bhi ziyada hon ge, aur is ki fazeelat aur bhi ziyada barh charh kar hogi"
  17,22,to Allah ke sath koi dosra mabood nah bana warna malamat zada aur be yaar o madad gaar betha reh jaayegaa
  17,23,"tairay rab ne faisla kar diya hai ke : tum log kisi ki ibadat nah karo, magar sirf uss ki walidain ke sath naik sulooq karo agar tumahray paas unn mein se koi aik, ya dono, boorhay ho kar rahen to inhen uf taq nah kaho, nah inhen jhirak kar jawab do, balkay un se ehtram ke sath baat karo"
  17,24,"aur narmi o reham ke sath un ke samnay jhuk kar raho, aur dua kya karo ke"" parvar-digaar, un par reham farma jis terhan unhon ne rehmat o shafqat ke sath mujhe bachpan mein paala tha """
  17,25,tumhara rab khoob jaanta hai ke tumahray dilon mein kya hai agar tum Saleh ban kar raho to woh aisay sab logon ke liye Dur guzar karne wala hai jo apne qasoor par mutnabba ho kar bandagi ke ravayye ki taraf palat ayen
  17,26,rishta daar ko is ka haq do aur maskeen aur musafir ko is ka haq fuzool kharchi nah karo
  17,27,"fuzool kharch log shetan ke bhai hain, aur shetan apne rab ka nashukara hai"
  17,28,"agar unn se ( yani haajat mand rishta daaron, miskeeno aur musafiron se ) tumhe katrana ho, is bana par ke abhi tum Allah ki uss rehmat ko jis ke tum umeed waar ho talaash kar rahay ho, to inhen naram jawab day do"
  17,29,nah to apna haath gardan se bandh rakho aur nah usay bilkul hi khula chore do ke malamat zada aur aajiz ban kar reh jao
  17,30,teer a rab jis ke liye chahta hai rizaq kushadah karta hai aur jis ke liye chahta hai tang kar deta hai woh apne bundon ke haal se bakhabar hai aur inhen dekh raha hai
  17,31,apni aulaad ko iflaas ke andaishay se qatal nah karo hum inhen bhi rizaq den ge aur tumhe bhi Dur haqeeqat unn ka qatal aik barri khata hai
  17,32,zina ke qareeb nah phutkowoh bohat bura feal hai aur bara hi bura rasta
  17,33,"qatal nafs ka irtikaab nah karo jisay Allah ne haraam kya hai magar haq ke sath aur jo shakhs mzlomanh qatal kya gaya ho is ke walii ko hum ne qisaas ke mutalbe ka haq ataa kya hai, pas chahiye ke woh qatal mein hadd se nah guzray, uss ki madad ki jaye gi"
  17,34,"ma l- yateem ke paas nah phutko magar Ahsen tareeqay se, yahan taq ke woh apne shabab ko poanch jaye ehad ki pabandi karo, be shak ehad ke baray mein tum ko jawab dahi karni hogi"
  17,35,"pemanay se do to poora bhar kar do, aur tolo to theek traazo se tolo yeh acha tareeqa hai aur bilhaaz injaam bhi yahi behtar hai"
  17,36,"kisi aisi cheez ke peechay nah lagu jis ka tumhe ilm nah ho yaqeenan aankhh, kaan aur dil sab hi ki baz purse honi hai"
  17,37,"zameen mein akarr kar nah chalo, tum nah zameen ko phaar satke ho, nah pahoron ki bulandi ko poanch satke ho"
  17,38,inn umoor mein se har aik ka bura pehlu tairay rab ke nazdeek napasandeedah hai
  17,39,yeh woh hikmat ki baatein hain jo tairay rab ne tujh par wahi ki hain aur dekh! Allah ke sath koi dosra mabood nah bana baith warna to jahannum mein daal diya jaye ga malamat zada aur har bhalai se mahroom ho kar
  17,40,kaisi ajeeb baat hai ke tumahray rab ne tumhe to beiton se nawaza aur khud apne liye mulaika ko betiyan bana liya? barri jhooti baat hai jo tum log zabanon se nikaltay ho
  17,41,"hum ne iss quran mein terhan terhan se logon ko samjhaya ke hosh mein ayen, magar woh haq se aur ziyada daur hi bhage ja rahay hain"
  17,42,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se kaho ke agar Allah ke sath dosray khuda bhi hotay, jaissa ke yeh log kehte hain, to woh maalik arsh ke maqam par pounchanay ki zaroor koshish karte"
  17,43,pak hai woh aur bohat baala o bartar hai unn baton se jo yeh log keh rahay hain
  17,44,"uss ki paki to saton aasman aur zameen aur woh saari cheezein bayan kar rahi hain jo aasman o zameen mein hain koi cheez aisi nahi jo is ki hamd ke sath is ki tasbeeh nah kar rahi ho, magar tum un ki tasbeeh samajte nahi ho haqeeqat yeh hai ke woh bara hi Burdbar aur dar guzar karne wala hai"
  17,45,jab tum quran parhte ho to hum tumahray aur akhirat par imaan nah laane walon ke darmain aik parda haail kar dete hain
  17,46,"aur un ke dilon par aisa ghilaaf charha dete hain ke woh kuch nahi samajte, aur un ke kaanon mein gharani peda kar dete hain aur jab tum quran mein apne aik hi rab ka zikar karte ho to woh nafrat se mun mourr letay hain"
  17,47,"hamein maloom hai ke jab woh kaan laga kar tumhari baat suntay hain to darasal kya suntay hain, aur jab baith kar baahum sargoshian karte hain to kya kehte hain yeh zalim aapas mein kehte hain ke yeh aik sehar zada aadmi hai jis ke peechay tum log ja rahay ho"
  17,48,"dekho, kaisi baatein hain jo yeh log tum par chant-tay hain yeh bhatak gay hain aِnhin rasta nahi milta"
  17,49,"woh kehte hain"" jab hum sirf haddiyan aur khaak ho kar reh jayen ge to kya hum naye suray se peda kar ke uthaye jayen ge? """
  17,50,"un se kaho"" tum pathar ya loha bhi ho jao"
  17,51,"ya is se bhi ziyada sakht koi cheez jo tumahray zehan mein qubool hayaat se baeed tar ho"" ( phir bhi tum uth kar raho ge ) woh zaroor poucheen ge"" kon hai woh jo hamein phir zindagi ki taraf palta kar laaye ga ?"" jawab mein kaho"" wohi jis ne pehli baar tum ko peda kya"" woh sir hila hila kar poucheen ge"" acha, to yeh hoga kab ?"" tum kaho"" kya ajab, woh waqt qareeb hi aa laga ho"
  17,52,"jis roz woh tumhe pukare ga to tum is ki hamd karte hue is ki pukaar ke jawab mein nikal aao ge aur tumhara gumaan uss waqt yeh hoga ke hum bas thori der hi iss haalat mein parre rahay hain """
  17,53,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, mere bundon se keh do ke zabaan se woh baat nikala karen jo behtareen ho darasal yeh shetan hai jo insanon ke darmain fasaad dalwanay ki koshish karta hai haqeeqat yeh hai ke shetan ansaa noon ka khula dushman hai"
  17,54,"tumhara rab tumahray haal se ziyada waaqif hai, woh chahay to tum par reham kere aur chahay to tumhe azaab day day aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne tum ko logon par hawala daar bana kar nahi bheja hai"
  17,55,"tera rab zameen aur asmano ki makhloqaat ko ziyada jaanta hai hum ne baaz payghambaroon ko baaz se barh kar martabay diye, aur hum ne hi DAWOD ko Zaboor di thi"
  17,56,"inn se kaho, pukaar dekho unn mabodon ko jin ko tum khuda ke siwa ( apna karsaaz ) samajte ho, woh kisi takleef ko tum se nah hata satke hain nah badal satke hain"
  17,57,jin ko yeh log pkarte hain woh to khud apne rab ke huzoor rasai haasil karne ka waseela talaash kar rahay hain ke kon uss se qareeb tar ho jaye aur woh uss ki rehmat ke umeed waar aur uss ke azaab se khaif hain haqeeqat yeh hai ke tairay rab ka azaab hai hi darny ke Laiq
  17,58,aur koi bastii aisi nahi jisay hum qayamat se pehlay halaak nah karen ya sakht azaab nah den yeh noshta Ellahi mein likha howa hai
  17,59,aur hum ko nishanain bhejnay se nahi roka magar is baat ne ke inn se pehlay ke log unn ko jhutla chuke hain ( chunancha dekh lau ) smod ko hum ne alania oontni laa kar di aur onhon ne is par zulm kya hum nishanain isi liye to bhaijtay hain ke log inhen dekh kar dareen
  17,60,"yaad karo ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne tum se keh diya tha ke tairay rab ne inn logon ko ghair rakha hai aur yeh jo kuch abhi hum ne tumhe dekhaya hai, iss ko aur uss darakht ko jis par quran mein laanat ki gayi hai, hum ne inn logon ke liye bas aik fitnah bana kar rakh diya hum aِnhin tanbeeh par tanbeeh kiye ja rahay hain, magar har tanbeeh inn ki sir kashi hi mein izafah kiye jati hai"
  17,61,"aur yaad karo jabkay hum ne mulaika se kaha ke aadam ko sajda karo, to sab ne sajda kya, magar iblees ne nah kya a seen ne kaha"" kya mein uss ko sajda karoon jisay to ne matti se banaya hai? """
  17,62,"phir woh bola"" dekh to sahi, kya yeh is qabil tha ke to ne isay mujh par fazeelat di? agar to mujhe qayamat ke din taq mohlat day to mein is ki poori nasal ki beekh kinny kar daloon, bas thoray hi log mujh se bach saken ge """
  17,63,"Allah taala ne farmaya"" acha to ja, un mein se jo bhi teri pairwi karen, tujh sameit unn sab ke liye jahannum hi bharpoor jaza hai"
  17,64,"to jis jis ko apni dawat se phsla sakta hai phsla le, un par apne sawaar aur payaday charha laa, maal aur aulaad mein un ke sath sajha laga, aur un ko wadon ke jaal mein phaans aur shetan ke waday aik dhokay ke siwa aur kuch bhi nahi"
  17,65,"yaqeenan mere bundon par tujhe koi Iqtidaar haasil nah hoga, aur tawakkal ke liye tera rab kaafi hai """
  17,66,tumhara ( haqeeqi ) rab to woh hai jo samandar mein tumhari kashti chalata hai taakay tum is ka fazl tala sh karo haqeeqat yeh hai ke woh tumahray haal par nihayat meharban hai
  17,67,"jab samandar mein tum par museebat aati hai to uss aik ke siwa dosray jin jin ko tum puraka karte ho woh sab gum ho jatay hain, magar jab woh tum ko bacha kar khushki par pouncha deta hai to tum uss se mun mourr jatay ho ensaan waqai bara nashukara hai"
  17,68,"acha, to kya tum iss baat se bilkul be khauf ho ke khuda kabhi khushki par hi tum ko zameen mein dhansa day, ya tum par pathrao karne wali aandhi bhaij day aur tum is se bachanay wala koi himayati nah pao ?"
  17,69,aur kya tumhe iss ka koi andesha nahi ke khuda phir kisi waqt samandar mein tum ko le jaye aur tumhari nashukri ke badlay tum par sakht tofani howa bhaij kar tumhe ghark kar day aur tum ko aisa koi nah miley jo uss se tumahray iss injaam ki pooch gach kar sakay ?
  17,70,yeh to hamari inayat hai ke hum ne bani aadam ko buzurgi di aur inhen khushki o tri mein swaryan ataa kee aur un ko pakeeza cheezon se rizaq diya aur apni bohat si makhloqaat par numaya foqiat bakhsh
  17,71,phir khayaal karo is din ka jab ke hum har insani giroh ko is ke peshwa ke sath bulayen ge uss waqt jin logon ko un ka nama aamaal seedhay haath mein diya gaya woh apna karnaama parheen ge aur un par zarra barabar zulm nah hoga
  17,72,aur jo iss duniya mein andha ban kar raha woh akhirat mein bhi andha hi rahay ga balkay rasta panay mein andhay se bhi ziyada nakaam
  17,73,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un logon ne iss koshish mein koi kasar utha nahi rakhi ke tumhe ftne mein daal kar uss wahi se phair den jo hum ne tumhari taraf bhaije hai taakay tum hamaray naam par apni taraf se koi baat gharro agar tum aisa karte to woh zaroor tumhe apna dost bana letay"
  17,74,aur baeed nah tha ke agar hum tumhe mazboot nah rakhtay to tum un ki taraf kuch nah kuch jhuk jatay
  17,75,"lekin agar tum aisa karte to hum tumhe duniya mein bhi dohray azaab ka maza chakhatay aur akhirat mein bhi dohray azaab ka, phir hamaray muqablay mein tum koi madadgaar nah paate"
  17,76,aur yeh log is baat par bhi taley rahay hain ke tumahray qadam iss sir zameen se ukhaar den aur tumhe yahan se nikaal bahar karen lekin agar yeh aisa karen ge to tumahray baad yeh khud yahan kuch ziyada der nah tehr saken ge
  17,77,"yeh hamara mustaqil tareeq car hai jo unn sab Rasolo-n ke muamlay mein hum ne brta hai jahin tum se pehlay hum ne bheja tha, aur hamaray tareeq car mein tum koi tagayur nah pao ge"
  17,78,namaz qaim karo zawaal aftaab se le kar andheray taq aur Fajar ke quran ka bhi iltazam karo kyunkay quran Fajar Mashhood hota hai
  17,79,"aur raat ko t_hjd parho, yeh tumahray liye Nafil hai, baeed nahi ke tumhara rab tumhe maqam Mahmood par Faiz kar day"
  17,80,"aur dua karo ke parvar-digaar, mujh ko jahan bhi to le ja sachaai ke sath le ja aur jahan se bhi nikaal sachaai ke sath nikaal aur apni taraf se aik Iqtidaar ko mera madadgaar bana day"
  17,81,"aur elaan kar do ke"" haq aa gaya aur baatil mit gaya, baatil to mitne hi wala hai """
  17,82,"hum iss quran ke silsila Tanzil mein woh kuch nazil kar rahay hain jo maan-ne walon ke liye to Shifa aur rehmat hai, magar zaalmon ke liye khasaray ke siwa aur kisi cheez mein izafah nahi karta"
  17,83,"ensaan ka haal yeh hai ke jab hum is ko Nemat ataa karte hain to woh inthtaaur peeth mourr laita hai, aur jab zara museebat se do chaar hota hai to mayoos honay lagta hai"
  17,84,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un logon se keh do ke"" har aik apne tareeqay par amal kar raha hai, ab yeh tumhara rab hi behtar jaanta hai ke seedhi raah par kon hai """
  17,85,"yeh log tum se rooh ke mutaliq puchhte hain kaho"" yeh rooh mere rab ke hukum se aati hai, magar tum logon ne ilm se kam hi behra paaya hai """
  17,86,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum chahain to woh sab kuch tum se chean len jo hum ne wahi ke zareya se tum ko ataa kya hai, phir tum hamaray muqablay mein koi himayati nah pao ge jo usay wapas dila sakay"
  17,87,"yeh to jo kuch tumhe mila hai tumahray rab ki rehmat se mila hai, haqeeqat yeh hai ke is ka fazl tum par bohat bara hai"
  17,88,"keh do ke agar ensaan aur jin sab ke sab mil kar is quran jaisi koi cheez laane ki koshish karen to nah laskin ge, chahay woh sab aik dosray ke madad gaar hi kyun nah hon"
  17,89,hum ne is quran mein logon ko terhan terhan se samjhaya magar aksar inkaar hi par jamay rahay
  17,90,"aur unhon ne kaha"" hum teer y baat nah manen ge jab taq ke to hamaray liye zameen ko phaar kar aik chashma jari nah kar day"
  17,91,ya tairay liye khajoron aur angarro ka aik baagh peda ho aur to is mein nhrin rawan kar day
  17,92,ya to asmano ko tukre tukre kar ke hamaray oopar gira day jaissa ke tera daawa hai ya khuda aur firshton ko roo Dur roo hamaray samnay le aeye
  17,93,"ya tairay liye sonay ka aik ghar ban jaye ya to aasman par charh jaye, aur tairay charhne ka bhi hum yaqeen nah karen ge jab taq ke to hamaray oopar aik aisi tehreer nah utaar laaye jisay hum parheen"" ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho"" pak hai mera parvar-digaar! kya mein aik pegham laane walay ensaan ke siwa aur bhi kuch hon? """
  17,94,"logon ke samnay jab kabhi hadaayat aayi to is par imaan laane se unn ko kisi cheez ne nahi roka magar unn ke isi qoul ne ke"" kya Allah ne bashar ko paighambar bana kar bhaij diya? """
  17,95,inn se kaho agar zameen mein farishtay itminan se chal phir rahay hotay to hum zaroor aasman se kisi farishtay hi ko unn ke liye paighambar bana kar bhaijtay
  17,96,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se keh do ke mere aur tumahray darmain bas aik Allah ki gawahi kaafi hai woh apne bundon ke haal se bakhabar hai aur sab kuch dekh raha hai"
  17,97,"jis ko Allah hadaayat day wohi hadaayat panay wala hai, aur jisay woh gumraahi mein daal day to uskay siwa aisay logon ke liye to koi haami o nasir nahi pa sakta un logon ko hum qayamat ke roz avndhe mun khech layein ge, andhay, gungay aur behray unn ka thikana jahannum hai jab kabhi is ki aag dheemi honay lagey gi hum usay aur bahrakna den ge"
  17,98,"yeh badla hai un ki is harkat ka ke unhon ne hamari ayaat ka inkaar kya aur kaha"" kya jab hum sirf haddiyan aur khaak ho kar reh jayen ge to naye suray se hum ko peda kar ke utha khara kya jaye ga? """
  17,99,"kya un ko yeh nah soojha ke jis khuda ne zameen aurAasmanon ko peda kya hai woh inn jeson ko peda karne ki zaroor qudrat rakhta hai? is ne inn ke hashar ke liye aik waqt muqarrar kar rakha hai jis ka aana yakeeni hai, magar zaalmon ko israar hai ke woh is ka inkaar hi karen ge"
  17,100,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho, agar kahin mere rab ki rehmat ke khazanay tumahray qabzay mein hotay to tum kharch ho jaane ke andaishay se zaroor un ko rok rakhtay waqai ensaan bara tang dil waqay howa hai"
  17,101,"hum ne moose ko to nishanain ataa ki theen jo Sarih tor par dikhayi day rahi theen ab yeh tum khud bani Israel se pooch lau ke jab woh samnay ayen to firaon ne yahi kaha tha na ke"" ae moose, mein samjhta hon ke to zaroor aik sehar zada aadmi hai """
  17,102,"moose ne is ke jawab mein kaha"" to khoob jaanta hai ke yeh baseerat Afroz nishanain Rab-us- Samwat -o -walarz ke siwa kisi ne nazil nahi ki hain, aur mera khayaal yeh hai ke ae firaon, to zaroor aik shamat zada aadmi hai """
  17,103,"aakhir kaar firaon ne iradah kya ke moose aur bani Israel ko zameen se ukhaar phainky, magar hum ne is ko aur iss ke sathiyon ko akhatta ghark kar diya"
  17,104,"aur is ke baad bani Israel se kaha ke ab tum zameen mein bso, phir jab akhirat ke waday ka waqt aan poora hoga to hum tum sab ko aik sath laa haazir karen ge"
  17,105,"is quran ko hum ne haq ke sath nazil kya hai aur haq hi ke sath yeh nazil howa hai, aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tumhe hum ne iss ke siwa aur kisi kaam ke liye nahi bheja ke ( jo maan le usay ) basharat day do aur ( jo nah manay ussay ) mutnabba kar do"
  17,106,"aur is quran ko hum ne thora thora kar ke nazil kya hai taakay tum tehr tehrkar usay logon ko sunaaoo, aur usay hum ne ( mauqa mauqa se ) batadreej utaara hai"
  17,107,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn logon se keh do ke tum usay manu ya nah manu, jin logon ko is se pehlay ilm diya gaya hai inhen jab yeh sunaya jata hai to woh mun ke bil sjday mein gir jatay hain"
  17,108,"aur pukaar uthte hain"" pak hai hamara rab, uss ka wada to poora hona hi tha """
  17,109,aur woh mun ke bil rotay hue gir jatay hain aur usay sun kar unn ka Khashoo aur barh jata hai
  17,110,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho, Allah keh kar poukaro ya Rehman keh kar, jis naam se bhi poukaro uss ke liye sab achay hi naam hain aur apni namaz nah bohat ziyada buland aawaz se parho aur nah bohat pust aawaz se, un dono ke darmain ost darjay ka lehja ikhtiyar karo"
  17,111,"aur kaho"" tareef hai is khuda ke liye jis ne nah kisi ko beta banaya, nah koi badshahi mein is ka shareek hai, aur nah woh aajiz hai ke koi is ka pshtiban ho"" aur is ki barayi bayan karo, kamaal darjay ki barayi"
